cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DC 

This paper is about training deep neural networks, which is a core topic in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also focuses on image classification tasks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper proposes a new training approach, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of adaptive batch sizes also involves optimization techniques, which could place the paper in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
